1. *Bog* je stvorio svet.(God created the world.)
2. *Boga* zaštiti od zla.(Protect God from evil.)
3. Ona moli *bogu* da joj pomogne.(She prays to God for help.)
4. Ona je verovala u *boga*.(She believed in God.)
5. Ona živi u strahu *boga*.(She lives in fear of God.)
6. Ona je hvalila *boga*.(She praised God.)
7. Ona je *bogu* zahvalna za sve što joj je dao.(She is thankful to God for all that he has given her.)
8. Oni su molili *bogu* da ih izbavi iz nedaće.(They prayed to God to deliver them from trouble.)